{Speech 7}{}{Hey, let me know when you get a promotion.@@I've got to go.@@Who the hell do you think you are, coming into our town?@@Just leave quietly, before anyone gets hurt.@@I don't like you.@@I just kill everybody who looks like you.}
{Speech 8}{}{What's your problem?@@Can't we work this out?@@Don't talk to me.@@Whatever it is, go tell somebody else.@@I don't think you're that tough.@@Why don't you just leave?}
{Speech 9}{}{Then I need to get some eggs.@@Do you know how to straighten out a tin wall?@@Hi.@@Don't pester me, please, I'm very busy.@@I wonder if there are any brahmin burgers left at Dusty's?@@Sometimes I forget where my head is.@@Umm... thanks, but I really must be going now.@@Maybe we'll finish later.@@Oh, yes, you're new in town.@@They say they'll be building new houses soon.@@Ever since Dumont was elected, the town has become very peaceful and quiet.@@Good day, stranger.@@You from the north? Not many northerners around here.@@I heard everybody from the wastes is a mutant or a savage!@@No time to chat. Got to work.@@You trade with Dappo? Oh, never mind, never mind.}
